phphaxor is a dark minimalistic syntax highlighting theme.
Specially made to light out your PHP code in between HTML/JS.

Am still working on toggling HTML / PHP highlighting, that will be in V1.0
For now just PHP is highlighted out.

Example: http://img169.imageshack.us/my.php?image=phphaxorv091kl0.png

